snippet.title: IncrediBubble (Windows game 2001)
snippet.description:
IncrediBubble is a 3D graphics tile-matching puzzle game by Suricate Software.
The object is to remove all bubbles in each level.
You can control the main player dolphin to shoot a bubble.

#puzzlegames #puzzlegamespc #puzzlegame
